nl_cmd: Place the vase on the bedside table in the bedroom.
Get the basketball from the floor by the bed and put it in the blue bin.

Take the pen that is next to the basketball and put it on the couch with the newspaper.
Take the alarm clock on the drawers in the bedroom and place it on the table in the study.
Take the remote control next to the clock on the small brown table and place it on the green armchair with the blue pillow opposite the TV.
Fetch the top book from the brown armchair and put it in the cardboard box in the corner of the room.
Pick up the spray and place it on the white stand with the plant on it.
Move to the bedroom. Take the teddy from the bed and place it on the yellow couch in the living room.
Pick up the pillow and place it on the other chair.

Take the basketball from beside the bed and place it beside the laptop on the table.
Pick up the remote from the couch. Put it on the drawer next to the vase.
Pick up the pot and place it by the TV, in the bin.
